	   <tr><td colspan=2>Actually, in order to get any of the specializations over 50 you need to have a point in ALL 5 of them. First one to get over 51 is the one that you can get to 200. If you leave any of them untrained however, the one you want at 200 will stay stuck at 50.<br><br>Faelawen Starfyre, the Mad Mage of Povar<br>&nbsp;<br></td></tr>
