	   <tr><td colspan=2>Hey Sparkle, welcome to the magehood LOL.&nbsp;&nbsp;Yes Malachite is the stone needed for your pet.  You will need 1 EACH time you summon a pet (in other words carry stacks(of20) as your money permits).  Malachite can be found in nearly every city I can think of, just look for the jewelry shop.  Also, some outposts thoughout sell them. Commons is a good example as well as RatheMountains.  You just need to check out or OOC to see if there is one.  Another spell you will need components for is when you get the 'Phantom' line of self ACbuffs. Phantom Leather, Phantom Chain, Phantom Plate, etc.  This spell takes 'CatsEye Agates'.  <br><br><br>Also, I noticed you mentioned Words.  There are some words you need to have for 'Research' once you reach Lvl16.  Research is god-awful to explain so check out some websites mentioned in these posts for info on it.  In short 'Research' will help you attain spells (mainly pets that I know of) that can't be bought from vendors).  Hope this helps a little.<br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
