	   <tr><td colspan=2>OK..here's my question and I have heard 50/50 for and against.&nbsp;&nbsp;Some say it's BS and some swear by it.  Do pets benefit from wearing 'Summoned Armor', what about the stats on 'Elemental Defender' &amp; 'Dagger of Symbols' ? do they affect the pet ?  Does a pet like Fire get any benefit from wearing the damage bracelett when he casts his DD spell ?.  Any proven replies will be greatly appreciated.<br><br>Wilee Castusmaximas 50Mage<br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
